channel.title: iPhone realtime voice changer (australia)
channel.description:
Hey,
I'm looking for a voice changer for my iPhone (change your voice during phone calls) for the obvious reason, prank calling friends.
I run a jailbroken, iOS4 iPhone. The problem is, I live in Australia and the programs available are for US/Canadians. Although there are ways to do it via an Aussie number, they charge international phone rates for the calls so it's out of the question.
Do you guys know of any that are available for Australians to make the calls for free and to Australian numbers?
